{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO838901B0324P1D1N001045", "chronotag": "1739874623103", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "I-1045", "numeroOrdreDepot": "1045", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "AN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO838901B0324P1D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0324", "triAmendement": "kfaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaafizj", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA793616", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845401", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": ["PA840075", "PA793432", "PA795778", "PA793672", "PA794570", "PA841487", "PA794954", "PA840801", "PA841955", "PA793362", "PA795786", "PA795974", "PA841563"]}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Mauvieux,  M.&#160;Casterman, M.&#160;Allisio, M.&#160;Jean-Philippe&#160;Tanguy, Mme&#160;Loir, M.&#160;Sabatou, M.&#160;Boulogne, M.&#160;Salmon, M.&#160;Fouquart, M.&#160;Renault, M.&#160;Gonzalez, Mme&#160;M&#233;nach&#233;, M.&#160;Lottiaux et Mme&#160;Marais-Beuil"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 32", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 32", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 32", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0324A.asp#D_Article_32"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"avant_A_Apres": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "numero": "1", "alineaDesignation": "Alin\u00e9a 1"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p>&#x00C0; la quatri&#x00E8;me ligne de la seconde colonne du tableau du premier alin&#x00E9;a, substituer au montant&nbsp;:</p><p>&#x00AB;&nbsp;30 000 000&nbsp;&#x00BB;,</p><p>le montant&nbsp;:&nbsp;</p><p>&#x00AB;&nbsp;8 000 000&nbsp;&#x00BB;.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>La Dotation de Compensation des Pertes de Bases de la Taxe Professionnelle et de la Redevance des Mines, mise en place pour aider les collectivit&#x00E9;s territoriales &#x00E0; compenser les pertes de recettes dues &#x00E0; la r&#x00E9;forme de la taxe professionnelle, n&#x2019;a plus l&#x2019;utilit&#x00E9; qu&#x2019;elle avait &#x00E0; l&#x2019;origine.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>En effet, la taxe professionnelle, qui constituait une source de financement essentielle pour les communes et leurs groupements, a &#x00E9;t&#x00E9; remplac&#x00E9;e par la Contribution Fonci&#x00E8;re des Entreprises (CFE) et la Cotisation sur la Valeur Ajout&#x00E9;e des Entreprises (CVAE). La suppression partielle de ces imp&#x00F4;ts de production a ensuite &#x00E9;t&#x00E9; compens&#x00E9;e par l&#x2019;affectation de recettes de l&#x2019;&#x00C9;tat aux collectivit&#x00E9;s.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Dans le cadre des efforts budg&#x00E9;taires que la France doit faire en 2025, nous souhaitons diminuer ces pr&#x00E9;l&#x00E8;vements sur les recettes de l&#x2019;&#x00C9;tat.&nbsp;</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-17", "datePublication": "2024-11-08", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Rejet\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-08T21:43:50+01:00", "sort": "Rejet\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO838901B0324P1D1N001045?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": "RUANR5L17S2025IDS28634", "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "4", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}